The single source of truth for agent instructions in this repo is
[AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) at the repo root.

Cursor does not follow symlinks reliably, so this rule file just points
you back. Read AGENTS.md before doing anything in this repo.

If the rules in AGENTS.md and these `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` files ever
conflict, AGENTS.md wins. File a bug to remove the divergence.
